      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Oct 1 article on Roche Holdings, which mischaracterized one of its drugs</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article last Sunday about the financial prospects of Roche Holding, the Swiss pharmaceuticals company, misidentified the disease that Pegasys, one of its medications in development, is intended to treat. It is hepatitis C, not B.</p>
      </block>
